.Dd $Mdocdate: August 24 2018 $
.Dt WHILE-BASIC 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm while-basic
.Nd the while request
.Sh DESCRIPTION
Loop with single-line scope:
.nr cnt 11 1
.de mym
\\n-[cnt]
..
.while \n[cnt] .mym
.Pp
Loop with multi-line scope, text line closure:
.nr cnt 11
.while \n[cnt] \{\
.nr cnt -1
\n[cnt]\},
boom.
.Pp
Loop with multi-line scope, macro line closure:
.nr cnt 11
.while \n[cnt] \{\
.nr cnt -1
\n[cnt]
.\}
.Pp
final text
